    "ja": "足跡"
  },
  "description": {
    "default": "Visited places on a map, ordered by visit date.",
    "en": "Visited places on a map, ordered by visit date.",
    "zh": "去过的地方在地图上画一条线。",
    "ja": "訪れた場所を地図上に時系列で記録。"
  },
  "docs": "# Footprint\n\n去过的地方打卡。每条 = {name, lat, lng, visited_at, note}。\n按 visited_at 升序连线展示足迹路线。\n\n经纬度获取：当前没有定位接口，需要自己手动填（从地图 app 复制 / Geocoding）。\n后续 v2 可以加 `app.locate` bridge action。\n",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "runtime": "auto",
  "author": "agent-rt",
  "category": "utilities",
  "keywords": [
    "travel",
    "map",
    "places",
    "footprint"
  ],
  "icon": "https://api.iconify.design/ph/map-pin-fill.svg?color=%23e91e63&width=256",
  "permissions": [
    "data:read",
    "data:write"
  ],
  "window": {
    "style": "phone",
    "width": 480,
    "height": 920
  },
  "collections": {
    "places": {
      "schema": {
        "name": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "lat": {
          "type": "number"
        },
        "lng": {
          "type": "number"
        },
        "visited_at": {
          "type": "number"
        },
        "note": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      },
      "indexes": [
        "visited_at",
        "name"
      ]
    }
  }
